data.description: Beautifully maintained and ready to move in!  Offering one level living on nearly 1/2 acre lot with huge fenced rear yard, detached storage.  Home wired  with subpanel for generator.Spacious screened porch and detached storage shed. Interior features include large living room with picture window, inviting family room with fireplace and brick wood burning fireplace.  Kitchen with pantry and ceiling fan.  Laundry/mudroom with shelving and access to screened porch. Three bedrooms, two bathrooms,  master with private bath.  All bedrooms have ceiling fans. Great storage area in pull down attic.   Just minutes to Lake Chesdin, Ft lee, 288, shopping and great schools.  See your new home today!
